SUMMARY:Seventh Circuit Court of Appeals Staff Attorney Panel
DESCRIPTION:You are invited to learn more about careers as a court staff 
 attorney. Like law clerks\, staff attorneys provide courts with procedura
 l and substantive legal advice regarding the disposition and efficient co
 mpletion of cases\, conduct research\, analyze cases\, draft memoranda an
 d orders\, and assist pro se litigants and counsel. Unlike law clerks\, s
 taff attorneys serve the court at large and not a single judge.Panelists 
 will include Aaron Petty\, supervising attorney\, and recent Maurer gradu
 ates George Glass and Zion Miller\, staff attorney clerks. Join to learn 
 more about their work and how they achieved their positions.Pizza will be
  served!
