 ily: 'Arial'\,sans-serif\; color: black\;">You are invited to learn more 
 about careers as a court staff attorney. Like law clerks\, staff attorney
 s provide courts with procedural and substantive legal advice regarding t
 he disposition and efficient completion of cases\, conduct research\, ana
 lyze cases\, draft memoranda and orders\, and assist pro se litigants and
  counsel. Unlike law clerks\, staff attorneys serve the court at large an
 d not a single judge.</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 10.0pt\; font-
 family: 'Arial'\,sans-serif\; color: black\;">Panelists will include Aaro
 n Petty\, supervising attorney\, and recent Maurer graduates George Glass
  and Zion Miller\, staff attorney clerks. Join to learn more about their 
 work and how they achieved their positions.</span></p><p><span style="fon
 t-size: 10.0pt\; font-family: 'Arial'\,sans-serif\; color: black\;">Pizza
  will be served!</span></p>
