SUMMARY:Prepare to Practice Workshop Series: General Research Refresher
DESCRIPTION:Looking forward to the end of exams and the start of your sum
 mer employment? Consider attending the Jerome Hall Law Library's "Prepare
  to Practice" workshop sessions!Each year\, the Jerome Hall Law Library o
 ffers a series of workshops and information sessions to help students pre
 pare for their summer positions. These sessions offer Maurer students an 
 opportunity to review\, refresh\, and refine their legal research techniq
 ues as they prepare for their summer roles. Each workshop focuses on rein
 forcing foundational skills\, exploring effective research approaches\, a
 nd helping students feel more confident in tackling real-world research t
 asks.If you have any questions\, please contact Morgan Kelly\, Student En
 gagement Librarian\, via email atkellyms@iu.edu.
