 attending the Jerome Hall Law Library's "Prepare to Practice" workshop se
 ssions!Each year\, the Jerome Hall Law Library offers a series of worksho
 ps and information sessions to help students prepare for their summer pos
 itions. These sessions offer Maurer students an opportunity to review\, r
