 heir summer roles. Each workshop focuses on reinforcing foundational skil
 ls\, exploring effective research approaches\, and helping students feel 
 more confident in tackling real-world research tasks.If you have any ques
 tions\, please contact Morgan Kelly\, Student Engagement Librarian\, via 
 email atkellyms@iu.edu.
