SUMMARY:ISBA Tax Panel
DESCRIPTION:The ISBA Tax Panel will feature several professionals from th
 e Indianapolis Bar who will discuss their experiences and career paths in
  tax law. Panelists will include attorneys practicing in different areas 
 of tax as well as judges who handle tax-related matters. The discussion w
 ill give students insight into the variety of roles available in the tax 
 field and how professionals navigate careers in both practice and the jud
 iciary. Attendees will also have the opportunity to ask questions and lea
 rn more about opportunities within the Indianapolis tax community.&#160\;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  The ISBA Tax Panel will feature several
  professionals from the Indianapolis Bar who will discuss their experienc
 es and career paths in tax law. Panelists will include attorneys practici
 ng in different areas of tax as well as judges who handle tax-related mat
 ters. The discussion will give students insight into the variety of roles
  available in the tax field and how professionals navigate careers in bot
 h practice and the judiciary. Attendees will also have the opportunity to
  ask questions and learn more about opportunities within the Indianapolis
  tax community.&#160\;</p>
