SUMMARY:Journal Ice Cream Social
DESCRIPTION:Join the editors of ILJ\, IJGLS\, and IJLSE for a joint Ice C
 ream Social in the Journal Office! This is the perfect chance for 1Ls to 
 get the inside scoop on the upcoming write-on competition\, learn about o
 ur respective journals\, and chat with current members in a relaxed setti
 ng. We'll be serving up treats to-go\, but there's a sweet twist: one luc
 ky student who picks the "winning" ice cream package will walk away with 
 a special prize! Whether you have specific questions or just want to meet
  your future colleagues over an ice cream sandwich\, we invite you to sto
 p by and explore the benefits of journal membership. We look forward to s
 eeing you there!&#160\;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Join the editors of ILJ\, IJGLS\, and I
 JLSE for a joint Ice Cream Social in the Journal Office! This is the perf
 ect chance for 1Ls to get the inside scoop on the upcoming write-on compe
 tition\, learn about our respective journals\, and chat with current memb
 ers in a relaxed setting. We'll be serving up treats to-go\, but there's 
 a sweet twist: one lucky student who picks the "winning" ice cream packag
 e will walk away with a special prize! Whether you have specific question
 s or just want to meet your future colleagues over an ice cream sandwich\
 , we invite you to stop by and explore the benefits of journal membership
 . We look forward to seeing you there!&#160\;</p>
